HEADWORD: Randan
<hw>Ran"dan</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧n"d⟦acr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
product of a second sifting of meal; the finest part of the bran.</def>
<mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Randan</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Randan
<hw>Ran"dan</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A boat propelled by three rowers
with four oars, the middle rower pulling two.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Randing</ent>⟦br⟧
